Usage: edit_bump_name [-help] -from <string> [-selected] -to <string>

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-from <string>     # Specifies the regular expression for the names of the
                   # bumps to be edited (string, required)
-selected          # Modify the name for selected bumps (bool, optional)
-to <string>       # Specifies the new name format for target bumps like a
                   # printf format (string, required)